ght be\nimportant. We conclude on recalling that, in the future, it will be mandatory\nto perform some complete multi-probes analyses, leaving the DE parameters as\nwell as the curvature as free parameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 Feb 2008 14:56:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 3 Dec 2008 11:31:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-06-23"}
